## 5. AI Solution Design

The MVP focuses on helping users identify housing listings where empadronamiento may be allowed. However, this information is rarely available as a structured filter on housing platforms.

Instead, empadronamiento compatibility is often hidden within listing descriptions written in natural language. Users must manually read each listing or contact landlords to confirm whether residency registration is possible.

To address this challenge, the product uses AI to analyze housing listings and detect signals indicating whether empadronamiento may be allowed.

The AI system performs the following functions:

• Analyze listing descriptions from housing platforms and social media posts  
• Detect phrases related to empadronamiento compatibility  
• Extract relevant housing information (price, location, accommodation type)  
• Convert unstructured listing text into structured signals  
• Surface housing opportunities compatible with the user’s preferences

