### 5.4 Key AI Tasks

The AI system performs several tasks to transform unstructured housing listings into structured opportunities compatible with empadronamiento.

| AI Task | Description | Product Value |
|---|---|---|
| Text Analysis | The system analyzes listing descriptions and captions from housing platforms and social media posts. | Allows the system to understand unstructured housing information. |
| Signal Detection | The AI detects phrases indicating whether empadronamiento may be allowed, negotiable, or unavailable. | Enables identification of listings compatible with administrative requirements. |
| Information Extraction | The system extracts structured information such as price, location, accommodation type, and minimum stay conditions. | Helps users quickly evaluate housing opportunities. |
| Opportunity Filtering | Listings are filtered based on detected signals and user preferences. | Surfaces the most relevant housing opportunities. |

### 5.5 Technical Approach

The system uses a combination of listing aggregation and AI-based text analysis to identify housing opportunities compatible with empadronamiento.

The technical approach focuses on analyzing unstructured listing descriptions and converting them into structured signals that can be used for filtering and discovery.

| Component | Technical Approach | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| Listing Collection | Listings are gathered from housing platforms and social media sources. | Aggregates housing opportunities from multiple channels. |
| Text Processing | Listing descriptions and captions are extracted for analysis. | Prepares unstructured text for AI processing. |
| AI Text Analysis | Natural language processing techniques are used to analyze listing content. | Enables the system to understand listing descriptions. |
| Signal Detection | Phrase detection is used to identify signals related to empadronamiento compatibility. | Detects whether residency registration may be allowed. |
| Structured Output | Extracted signals and listing attributes are converted into structured data. | Allows listings to be filtered and presented to users. |
